data.description: NEW LOW Price!!! This updated Reynolsburg Schools, RANCH home offers a delightful living space that has been upgraded with all-new carpeting and has been treated to a fresh coat of paint, creating a bright & modern feel. Freshly painted throughout as well! No need to worry about the hassle of appliance shopping - your new home includes newer Stainless Steel kitchen appliances & washer & dryer can stay! The expansive fenced-in yard is a standout feature, offering a private oasis where you can unwind, entertain, or let your pets roam. New water softener & a reverse osmosis system. Experience the benefits of purified and softened water throughout the entire home!This home qualifies for up to $7,500 of paid buyer closing cost +3% down payment down payment grant up to $10,000!
